{"tid":2512622,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港警察玩交友app被騙20萬","createTime":"2021-05-02T01:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T23:42:19.000Z","uid":54337,"like":86,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"c7c58d0ad8d144ae8352ae5bd940e876aa105a16","tid":2512622,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:22:07.000Z","msg":"一名駐守長沙灣警署的男警疑墮網上情緣騙案。據知該名男警駐守長沙灣警署，平日於報案室工作，入職1至2年，去年他透過交友App認識一名女子，二人相談甚歡，但一直未能見面，對方更聲稱因疫情關係，一直滯留日本，未能回港，急需金錢應急。<br />\n<br />\n男警得悉後，先後多次匯款予對方，合共約20萬元，至今年4月，該名男警與女網友失去聯絡，始知受騙，於是向上級尋求協助，之後到元朗警署報案。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，元朗警署昨日（4月30日）接獲一名男子報案，指懷疑被人騙去合共約20萬港元，案件列作以欺騙手段取得財產，由元朗警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n近年網上情緣騙案有持續上升趨勢，根據警方數字，去年共有905宗，較2019年上升逾五成，損失金額達2.1億元。同類騙案涉及的手法亦多變，本報早前則踢爆在疫情下美容院被數度勒令停業，疑有推銷集團伺機擴展掠水業務殺入中醫界，有「中醫妹」經交友App釣客，噓寒問暖故作曖昧，目的為氹客購買中醫療程，即使事主無病無痛，仍被游說幫襯逾萬元、長達一年的中醫療程。中醫妹更會連環劏客，數日內再推銷過萬元的教育課程。"},{"pid":"1b3e2c0e9bc87dbcc89eabbff7a17b09665b7e78","tid":2512622,"uid":130438,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:23:43.000Z","msg":"其實比人呃左都算 點解佢仲自爆呢<br />\n明知無可能拎得返"},{"pid":"0ee4f25ea661d0bab4da2eabb5aad6acc9ca073c","tid":2512622,"uid":3177,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:23:50.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">抵啦 年中咁多人中 黑驚中招 又查唔查到啊</span>"},{"pid":"17c1f21e2212d9fb9214aa61fdca165bd4840c54","tid":2512622,"uid":54337,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:24:53.000Z","msg":"昨晚見到有人post<br />\n但極速沉底<br />\npr效率真係高<br />\n我唯有重post"},{"pid":"6ce3e624c270a568a18a39d1606bb45a3a111b07","tid":2512622,"uid":54337,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:26:23.000Z","msg":"跌左20萬<br />\n問琛哥攞返囉<br />\n大家係一家人嗎"},{"pid":"de826a6d4789e054b8dfedaac27d04acc2289884","tid":2512622,"uid":258340,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"1b3e2c0e9bc87dbcc89eabbff7a17b09665b7e78","tid":2512622,"uid":130438,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:23:43.000Z","msg":"其實比人呃左都算 點解佢仲自爆呢<br />\n明知無可能拎得返"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:29:43.000Z","msg":"醒就唔會做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7485d4062a695d5ac20524fc38c4249861e18008","tid":2512622,"uid":241171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:31:58.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24001d7b2cb34052640d1921782a33e0032e6208","tid":2512622,"uid":66324,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:32:46.000Z","msg":"係咪做popo比朋友排太寂寞"},{"pid":"7f94466b2b2e528dc951eede2d64074d850e9712","tid":2512622,"uid":247893,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:38:54.000Z","msg":"提子提子"},{"pid":"efe8b082ba7a68985c328a722832f8c07e0e54cd","tid":2512622,"uid":93277,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:40:51.000Z","msg":"ON9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己日日係報案室都見唔少呢D案啦，佢唔係以為自己好獨特遇真愛呀麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc320ed3332dfb386743a0a87dd5a589a8b6f4b0","tid":2512622,"uid":132488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de826a6d4789e054b8dfedaac27d04acc2289884","tid":2512622,"uid":258340,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"1b3e2c0e9bc87dbcc89eabbff7a17b09665b7e78","tid":2512622,"uid":130438,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:23:43.000Z","msg":"其實比人呃左都算 點解佢仲自爆呢<br />\n明知無可能拎得返"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:29:43.000Z","msg":"醒就唔會做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:43:15.000Z","msg":"仲要俾上級知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3f8addb6d2f7f812bd7db378dfdf873c1cc7ed","tid":2512622,"uid":26154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efe8b082ba7a68985c328a722832f8c07e0e54cd","tid":2512622,"uid":93277,"like":14,"d